    {
      "chinese": "大武部落中，較常見的儀式禮品有二：一、在進行結婚儀式的前一、兩天不等，會殺豬作牲禮、小米糕、灌腸，準備佳餚。結婚當天，則帶著所預備的禮品，如作物、飲料及飾品等，和聘禮一起由對方（女）確認，女方滿意後，才宣布接受，開始婚禮慶典。",
      "ab": "ikai naiya ka taiLabuwa, ku ngikakalralemadu kipailuku ka twahahukudra taidrusaa. ku sakataingeaa- mahudrange, luaikahudrange twahahukudra, waculu ku beeke, twadrete, twaabai, twaakanea tudamai padulru ku satulrevega, lapakane pakisupilri pakihagai ki kinauwacekela. lu amaninga idra vai, wailuku idra nipadulruwa ka hahukudra, paelre ku lasaungula si talahaedre, palungu, cinakacakaha ka lrabu, makaelaela ka lamanema si lasabadha, mwaki taliababadha akuea wasipi, lu palraingi ku taliababadha twalrepenge si pathagili kapeapehau.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2024/09/09/7ffe2f4286fa7e46f92f93bce4aa8b19.mp3",
